{"pv28:0.1":"Petavatthu ","pv28:0.2":"Culavagga ","pv28:0.3":"3. Rathakarapetivatthu ","pv28:1.1":"“Veluriyathambham ruciram pabhassaram, ","pv28:1.2":"Vimanamaruyha anekacittam; ","pv28:1.3":"Tatthacchasi devi mahanubhave, ","pv28:1.4":"Pathaddhani pannaraseva cando. ","pv28:2.1":"Vanno ca te kanakassa sannibho, ","pv28:2.2":"Uttattarupo bhusa dassaneyyo; ","pv28:2.3":"Pallankasetthe atule nisinna, ","pv28:2.4":"Eka tuvam natthi ca tuyha samiko. ","pv28:3.1":"Ima ca te pokkharani samanta, ","pv28:3.2":"Pahutamalya bahupundarika; ","pv28:3.3":"Suvannacunnehi samantamotthata, ","pv28:3.4":"Na tattha panko panako ca vijjati. ","pv28:4.1":"Hamsa cime dassaniya manorama, ","pv28:4.2":"Udakasmimanupariyanti sabbada; ","pv28:4.3":"Samayya vaggupanadanti sabbe, ","pv28:4.4":"Bindussara dundubhinamva ghoso. ","pv28:5.1":"Daddallamana yasasa yasassini, ","pv28:5.2":"Navaya ca tvam avalamba titthasi; ","pv28:5.3":"Alarapamhe hasite piyamvade, ","pv28:5.4":"Sabbangakalyani bhusam virocasi. ","pv28:6.1":"Idam vimanam virajam same thitam, ","pv28:6.2":"Uyyanavantam ratinandivaddhanam; ","pv28:6.3":"Icchamaham nari anomadassane, ","pv28:6.4":"Taya saha nandane idha moditun”ti. ","pv28:7.1":"“Karohi kammam idha vedaniyam, ","pv28:7.2":"Cittanca te idha nihitam bhavatu; ","pv28:7.3":"Katvana kammam idha vedaniyam, ","pv28:7.4":"Evam mamam lacchasi kamakaminin”ti. ","pv28:8.1":"“Sadhu”ti so tassa patissunitva, ","pv28:8.2":"Akasi kammam tahim vedaniyam; ","pv28:8.3":"Katvana kammam tahim vedaniyam, ","pv28:8.4":"Upapajji so manavo tassa sahabyatanti. ","pv28:9.1":"Rathakarapetivatthu tatiyam. ","pv28:9.2":"Bhanavaram dutiyam. "}